title: Requiem 1.8.8 DRM Remover for iTunes 8.1
description:
Requiem 1.8.8 DRM Remover for iTunes 8.1 (Mac (Intel only) and Windows)

- Changes since last version -

1.8.7 -> 1.8.8:
- bug fix: copy tail of file correctly.


For more information, see
http://hymn-project.org/forums/viewtopic.php?t=2494

This program is not intended to promote piracy.  It only works with files you have legally purchased. Do not expect it to work with rentals.

Do not redistribute your decrypted media files, especially because they still contain identifying information.
